Unix.*.Gui.StatusFont:      -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
WinNT.*.Gui.DefaultFont:     -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-*-*-15-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
